vulnerability.name: USN-6487-1
vulnerability.description: Evgeny Vereshchagin discovered that Avahi contained several reachable  assertions, which could lead to intentional assertion failures when  specially crafted user input was given. An attacker could possibly use this issue to cause a denial of service. (CVE-2023-38469, CVE-2023-38470, CVE-2023-38471, CVE-2023-38472, CVE-2023-38473)

statements.status_notes: Avahi could be made to crash if it received specially crafted input.
